[32m+[m[32m## [1.0.13] - 2025-01-17[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### âœ¨ New Radius Controls[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m#### Added[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **`.rSafe` extension** â€“ gently clamped radius scaling that keeps corners natural across devices.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **`SKRadiusMode`** â€“ configure radius behavior (`safe`, `scaled`, `fixed`) for all `SKit.rounded*` helpers.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **`ScaleValueFactory.createRadiusSafe()` / `createBorderRadiusSafe()`** â€“ cached safe radius computations.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **`ScaleManager.getRadiusSafe()`** â€“ configurable clamp bounds with `setRadiusSafeBounds()`.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m#### Changed[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- `SKit.rounded`, `roundedContainer`, and `roundedContainerSize` now default to `SKRadiusMode.safe`.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Numeric radius size helpers now avoid auto-scaling raw doubles, keeping design intent intact.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Example app updated to demonstrate `.rSafe`, `.r`, and `.rFixed` usage, with new guidance cards.[m
[32m+[m[32m- README extension section expanded with radius helper comparison and new code samples.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Added `radiusMode` documentation across helper methods.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m#### Fixed[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Prevented oversized corner rounding on wide desktop/tablet layouts when using design radii (e.g., 12 now clamps to 15 max).[m
[32m+[m[32m- Ensured border-radius caching respects new safe/fixed behaviors without recomputation.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### ðŸ“š Documentation[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Installation instructions updated to `^1.0.13`.[m
[32m+[m[32m- New README guidance on choosing `.rSafe`, `.r`, or `.rFixed`.[m
[32m+[m[32m- Example snippets highlight `radiusMode` usage and stable radius tips.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m---[m
